        "timestamp": "2018-12-18 10:41:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\nLooks like this commit introduces a bug after all (missed that in reviews).\nIt uses port 30263 in multicloud/charts/multicloud-prometheus/charts/prometheus-grafana/values.yaml which is also used in sdc-dcae-fe chart (and is allicated in node-port wiki page to sdc)\nThis causes sdc to fail to deploy.",
