        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\n> > Looks like this commit introduces a bug after all (missed that in\n > > reviews).\n > > It uses port 30263 in multicloud/charts/multicloud-prometheus/charts/prometheus-grafana/values.yaml\n > > which is also used in sdc-dcae-fe chart (and is allicated in\n > > node-port wiki page to sdc)\n > > This causes sdc to fail to deploy.\n > \n > At the time, this port was available. I will update with a new port\n > that is free. We really need to move away from nodeports to an\n > ingress gateway or some other alternative.\n\nActually, I didn't find a free port in the wiki in 302xx range. Should we possibly move all multicloud to 304xx range?",
